{"tid":143033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉獲女兒安慰：特首唔做都罷 分分鐘要坐監","createTime":"2017-03-04T09:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T12:06:01.000Z","uid":48093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7893a9850d80245c3315908130cb1e68f224ea6","tid":143033,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"西環吹雞，逾200名建制派選委未有提名任何人下，葉劉淑儀連續兩屆特首選舉，均未能取得150票提名，宣佈棄選。她昨日在電台節目透露，女兒安慰她，特首之位很高危，「唔做就罷啦，分分鐘要坐監添」，似乎暗指前特首曾蔭權因行為失當罪成入獄。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉在節目被問到會否參與下屆特首選舉時，未有正面回應，只是說特首一職不易做，「呢份工都好難做，所以我個女同我講唔做就罷啦，分分鐘要坐監添，呢份工咁高危，misconduct（行為失當）範圍好闊」。"},{"pid":"8d7162e985fe688a267f989f424fc2bcacc18344","tid":143033,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:49:20.000Z","msg":"強酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8c7ab32645571aa9736b9ba1928b89da84b87e","tid":143033,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"係就宣佈終身唔參選啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc66f5a55eafdecdfa77103dff49656cbbf2ec5","tid":143033,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"有其女必有母"},{"pid":"bc61acb500745f0ddd605ccf5967b69fe5224298","tid":143033,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:17:01.000Z","msg":"豬女兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7748977abd0a8fc39feadfef4aa2280e7884965","tid":143033,"uid":9574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"吃不到的葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625694bb3953fa4c42741dfb35b78d6e68874617","tid":143033,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86c19d23a39ea78f1292303864ca1bdaeddd3b6","tid":1430